OL,3,CFour new ambulances delivered to
OL,4,CHatzola after arson attack
OL,6,FFour Government-loaned ambulances have
OL,7,Farrived in a north-west London suburb
OL,8,Fto replace Jewish community ambulances
OL,9,Fthat were destroyed in an arson attack.
OL,11,FThe London Ambulance Service vehicles
OL,12,Farrived at a car park in Golders Green
OL,13,Fat around 1.20pm on Tuesday afternoon.
OL,15,FIt followed Health Secretary Wes
OL,16,FStreeting announcing on Monday that
OL,17,Fthe LAS would loan the vehicles to
OL,18,FHatzola after four of the charity's
OL,19,Fambulances were set on fire in the
OL,20,Fearly hours of the morning.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
