OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774447876
OL,3,CFour new ambulances delivered to
OL,4,CHatzola after arson attack
OL,6,FThe Government will also cover the
OL,7,Fcost of the vehicles that were
OL,8,Fdestroyed, Mr Streeting announced.
OL,10,FAfter the LAS vehicles parked, Hatzola
OL,11,Fchairman Shloimie Richman read out a
OL,12,Fstatement saying Monday was the
OL,13,F"darkest day" in the charity's
OL,14,Fexistence.
OL,16,F"Hatzola Northwest is a volunteer led
OL,17,Fcommunity ambulance service that has
OL,18,Fbene in existence since 1984.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774447876
OL,3,CFour new ambulances delivered to
OL,4,CHatzola after arson attack
OL,6,F"The arson that took place during the
OL,7,Fearly hours of of Monday morning was
OL,8,Fthe start of the darkest day in the
OL,9,Fclose to fifty years of our existence.
OL,11,F"Who would ever dream that ambulances
OL,12,Fto provide emergency care and save
OL,13,Flives should the target of this
OL,14,Fheinous attack?"
OL,16,FA member of the London Ambulance
OL,17,FService was also present and addressed
OL,18,Fthe crowd, saying:" Anti-Semitism has
OL,19,Fno place in our society.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774447876
OL,3,CFour new ambulances delivered to
OL,4,CHatzola after arson attack
OL,6,F"Despite this tragic event that has
OL,7,Foccurred, we stand shoulder to
OL,8,Fshoulder with Hatzola and feel pleased
OL,9,Fto be able to support them today with
OL,10,Fthese four ambulances that you can see
OL,11,Fin front of you here.
OL,13,F"We look forward to continuing to work
OL,14,Fand deliver healthcare to Londoners,
OL,15,Fwith Hatzola as our partners, as we
OL,16,Fhave done and we're really pleased to
OL,17,Fbe able to support them at this time."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
