OL,3,CFour new ambulances delivered to
OL,4,CHatzola after arson attack
OL,6,FFundraisers have raise over 1 million
OL,7,Fpounds for the charity and speaking to
OL,8,FITV News, Mr Richman expressed what
OL,9,Fthat meant to volunteers like him.
OL,11,FHe said: "It means that we are a
OL,12,Fservice that the community and the
OL,13,Fpublic, understand and respect and
OL,14,Frealise is essential to their everyday
OL,15,Flife."
